    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features the original, deep-gloss factory paint, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracks. Mechanically, it is flawless, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule with all records meticulously organized. There are no leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power just as it did on the showroom floor. Every button, sensor, and feature functions perfectly. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated collector-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
