    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this exemplary specimen, presented in impeccable condition. This vehicle has been meticulously curated and maintained to a showroom standard, exhibiting no discernible wear. It represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a flagship-grade asset that performs with the precision and aesthetic integrity of a new arrival. This is an uncompromising choice for those who demand the finest in automotive excellence.",
